Package: langnetr
Type: Package
Title: Creates a language network based on similarity 
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Cynthia", "Siew", email = "cynsiewsq@gmail.com",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Cynthia Siew <cynsiewsq@gmail.com>
Description: Converts a list of words into a language network. 
    Each node in the network is one word in the list. 
    Edges are placed between pairs of words with edit distance = 1.
    List of words can be either phonological transcriptions or orthographic representations.
    Outputs an igraph object for further analysis.
License: Anyone can use it. 
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports: 
    dplyr,
    igraph,
    stringdist
URL: http://github.com/csqsiew/langnetr 
